Device-FTDI

PREREQUISITES

In order to build this module you have to install libftdi development
packages. See http://www.intra2net.com/en/developer/libftdi/

INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

	perl Makefile.PL
	make
	make test
	make install

SUPPORT AND DOCUMENTATION

After installing, you can find documentation for this module with the
perldoc command.

    perldoc Device::FTDI

